data.description: Spacious and well maintained 2 bdrm. 2 baths, with over 1,000 sq ft living space.  Located in the West Tower.  Renovations done in 2021 includes ungraded bathrooms, quartz counters in kitchen. plumbing fixtures in kitchen & baths, vinyl plank flooring in kitchen & bathrooms, paint and drapery. Building has sprinklers.  Panoramic golf course and mountain views.  No afternoon sun. 1 covered parking in a secured garage conviently located near entry gate, with ample guest parking. Amenities include:  Tennis courts, pool, BBQ, private park area.
